            <a:pPr indent="0" marL="0"><a:buNone/></a:pPr>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="92400E"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t xml:space="preserve">Health tier thresholds are industry starting points, not PANW-validated. </a:t></a:r>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="4A5568"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>The 5%/40%/80%/120% breakpoints need 12–18 months of PANW cohort data to validate. Until then, thresholds are calibrated, not proven.</a:t></a:r>
          </a:p>
        </p:txBody>
      </p:sp>

