            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="4A5568"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>A customer burning credits on idle workloads looks identical to active threat response. Engagement quality signal (alerts acted on, policies deployed) is a v2 addition.</a:t></a:r>
          </a:p>
        </p:txBody>
      </p:sp>

