            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="065F46"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t xml:space="preserve">SCD Type 1 in v1 overwrites territory history. </a:t></a:r>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="4A5568"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>Territory reassignment history is lost. Cohort reporting by original territory is unreliable until SCD Type 2 is implemented in v2.</a:t></a:r>
