            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" b="1" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="991B1B"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t xml:space="preserve">Comp integration is infrastructure-ready but process-blocked. </a:t></a:r>
            <a:r><a:rPr lang="en-US" sz="1200" dirty="0"><a:solidFill><a:srgbClr val="4A5568"/></a:solidFill></a:rPr><a:t>The data model is built. But Finance and RevOps must define the correction workflow, clawback policy, and dispute process before the first live comp period. CFO sign-off required on retroactive corrections.</a:t></a:r>
